SlateMind,is,a,mind,mapping,tool,that,runs,off,of,the,Slatebox,application,platform,It,allows,teams,to,collaboratively,map,out,ideas,visually,on,a,blank,slate,It,is,marketing,toward,teachers,and,businesses,as,an,easy,to,use,tool,for,conveying,ideas,The,SlateMind,API,is,a,simple,querying,tools,for,retrieving,publically,available,slates